- It's going to be funny when

- Okay, can you just hang on a second?

they were going to get the
quarterback Bo Callahan,
but they don't get him, right?

- [Woman] And like you

with skin as pale as mine
would, like, look good.
- You know I can't hear you right?
Everything you're saying I can't hear.

- [Woman] Oh, I'm sorry.
Am I annoying you?

- No, it's just that if you
want to have a conversation
Turn around, look at my dance.
Bam, bam, bam bam bam, bam bam, one, two!
- You love me, kiss me, you love me.

You're going to need to
get in the other lane.
- You told me not to backseat drive.

- [Woman] I think we should
move the desk into the bedroom.

I mean it saves room in
the other room and...

- I got a dance, it goes
like this. I got a dance...

- I think it's like a
baby shower or something.

- You think it's like a
baby shower or something?
- Do you bring stuff to those?
Oh! Can I put these in your bag?
- Will Momma give Daddy another drink?
- Momma gives Daddy whatever he wants!

- Couples that do baby
talk are so annoying.

- Right? I mean, this
is just embarrassing.
